ou can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":72,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBUQ040EGAYiEwi-8JaWuOuTAxV-4JQJHfFFPGRIneWswtHe3qc3ygEEUofGig==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXplNkpQNFcwNnZPM0hsWWdYWVV1a3ZhZGVZQXxBQ3Jtc0tucjQ1UE9SdVlEVVJ3WnZnWGh6OEJqd3pDWEVVQnFpTjkxWG5wWUNXR3BZVXY1bjR0ZHd3V3d2RHM0RFlGQ2pDcnp4dUpMUV9nWXY2RGczSmVkV0h4bFRUSENZRFluaTFOVTZ0Q2lpazUybkp0RlUyTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=N0969RhLMp0","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbXplNkpQNFcwNnZPM0hsWWdYWVV1a3ZhZGVZQXxBQ3Jtc0tucjQ1UE9SdVlEVVJ3WnZnWGh6OEJqd3pDWEVVQnFpTjkxWG5wWUNXR3BZVXY1bjR0ZHd3V3d2RHM0RFlGQ2pDcnp4dUpMUV9nWXY2RGczSmVkV0h4bFRUSENZRFluaTFOVTZ0Q2lpazUybkp0RlUyTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=N0969RhLMp0","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":184,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBUQ040EGAYiEwi-8JaWuOuTAxV-4JQJHfFFPGRIneWswtHe3qc3ygEEUofGig==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbjdVbTM4cFlIalZvQnVGSlBYOEpuXy1zVzNoQXxBQ3Jtc0trSG04RWx4cHh5ZVRBMW0tT3R0VENpbjBhU3pJdFpaWHRtX3JQYzRBVlFzWE13S3BDazNHMDdkZk5uZ1oxY2lCaUtSZnlWMTZ0RG1pcnh3V1R6WWhjb3ZVS3